and  i  thought , why  not  take  this  and  connect  it  to  my  digital  scan  data  and  have  google  earth  for  my  body ? what  did  google  come  out  with  this  year ? now  there  's  google  body  browser .
but  you  see , it  's  still  generic .
it  's  not  my  data .
